scenes.description: Promotional slideshow featuring hololive English 3rd Concert 'All for One' merchandise, including the Essentials Pack, Light Stick, and T-shirts.
A montage of digital messages and illustrations from fans expressing their excitement and support for the concert.
Advertisements for upcoming events: 'On the Run!' Advent 2nd Anniversary Live and 'ZOM-RAID TIME' featuring Kureiji Ollie.
Information screen stating the concert will start soon, highlighting the official hashtag #holoAllForOne.
Visitor attention slide regarding flashing light effects and cheering guidelines.
Final rotation of the concert merchandise slides.
